{"tid":47932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇鼻敏感嘅巴絲入黎幫手解決下我嘅問題","createTime":"2016-12-20T16:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T19:29:47.000Z","uid":40487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4635efbbc1038c05c5dcd860db3bdc3f5977111c","tid":47932,"uid":40487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:48:54.000Z","msg":"小弟由細到大都係咁<br />\n<br />\n每次係好焗嘅場所/地方都會突然狂流鼻水，流完一陣就會不停打乞嚏，之後就鼻塞，一時左塞一時右塞，塞完一邊到一邊，有時仲會兩個一齊塞，呼吸勁辛苦，逼住要用口抖氣<br />\n<br />\n有次訓訓下突然醒左，發現自己兩邊鼻都完全塞，冇風出同入，個下嚇死好驚自己會有咩事<br />\n<br />\n會唔會有巴絲知道解決方法可以話比我聽<br />\n夏天好嚴重，宜家冬天都仲好焗好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854660709f2719bce7a83f77bca96fbd21d00942","tid":47932,"uid":40487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978781888266a3d155f8d61b759f7f395025a02e","tid":47932,"uid":62806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:23:30.000Z","msg":"岩啊，由細到大都係咁真係好煩😑<br />\n凍啲又唔得，熱啲又唔得，轉天氣就最煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個鼻塞到嚇死人，想舒服咁訓都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5fe8ebbe249407a6d53c23d8dea38ccf9866d5","tid":47932,"uid":67938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟由細到大都係咁<br />\n<br />\n每次係好焗嘅場所/地方都會突然狂流鼻水，流完一陣就會不停打乞嚏，之後就鼻塞，一時左塞一時右塞，塞完一邊到一邊，有時仲會兩個一齊塞，呼吸勁辛苦，逼住要用口抖氣<br />\n<br />\n有次訓訓下突然醒左，發現自己兩邊鼻都完全塞，冇風出同入，個下嚇死好驚自己會有咩事<br />\n<br />\n會唔會有巴絲知道解決方法可以話比我聽<br />\n夏天好嚴重，宜家冬天都仲好焗好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開窗等空氣流通啲會唔會好啲？<br />\n我自己真係頂唔順嘅話會食抗旼敏藥，都幾work"},{"pid":"63530197cfbb8564197bd5ae30a08c30051c4d98","tid":47932,"uid":24637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:47:01.000Z","msg":"我由細到大個鼻都有一邊係塞 噴唔到氣 有無人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ca0bbed54bdaf3fa0cc17d3b3475f31e74fdf3","tid":47932,"uid":50815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T19:08:58.000Z","msg":"認真食蜂膠好有用<br />\n我由細到大都有鼻塞<br />\n最近食撚左蜂膠冇鼻塞"},{"pid":"4059aece13df5911c3703278eee329bbc9b8f459","tid":47932,"uid":27671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T19:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真食蜂膠好有用<br />\n我由細到大都有鼻塞<br />\n最近食撚左蜂膠冇鼻塞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊到買同邊隻好？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e472beebfb3fc5c88638bad146b6e8143ef887","tid":47932,"uid":52112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T19:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真食蜂膠好有用<br />\n我由細到大都有鼻塞<br />\n最近食撚左蜂膠冇鼻塞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊到買同邊隻好？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同求"}]}